text: Govinda Bahadur Shrestha (1939 - November 12, 2016) was the Chief Justice of Nepal from 22 January 2004 to 13 January 2005. == References == Category:Chief Justices of Nepal Category:Nepalese judges Category:Justices of the Supreme Court of Nepal Category:1939 births Category:2016 deaths
